msgid "Closing the Pocket"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/name_big"
msgid "Closing the Pocket"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/01"
msgid "Comrades! Today is the day of reckoning for the Hitlerite hordes! Whilst our glorious 5th Guards Tank Army is breaching the Fascist defenses around Memel, we will secure this area and cut them off. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/02"
msgid "The Germans attacked us last night, and today you are to counter-attack and drive them out of this sector. "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/03"
msgid "Expect high enemy presence, as they will be armed to the teeth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/04"
msgid "There are certain key locations in the area which the High Command expects to be captured. I will divert additional troops and resources to your command as you progress with your mission. Good luck, comrades! Onward, to victory!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/05"
msgid "The Luftwaffe may make an appearance. You must always advance with support from the AA guns. Our forward observers will inform when enemy ground-attack aircraft are inbound."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/06"
msgid "An enemy column is bound to arrive shortly, from the south! Get ready to greet them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task1_complete"
msgid "Good job. You now have access to supplies and logistical vehicles."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task2_complete"
msgid "Excellent. AT-guns and other support weaponry are now at your disposal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task3_complete"
msgid "The Fascists have been driven out of the settlement once and for all! You now have command of our medium tanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task4_complete"
msgid "Nothing can stop our glorious Red Army. And now nothing will stop your heavy tanks, comrade. Use them wisely, we don't have many of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task5_complete"
msgid "Those miserable Hitlerite lowlives will no longer be able to bombard our neighboring regiments. Comrade, I am giving you command of our long-range weaponry reserves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task6_complete"
msgid "These Fascists have excellent radio equipment. We will use their equipment to relay ground attack coordinates for our Sturmoviks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task7_complete"
msgid "The enemy headquarters are ours. The end of the Fascist occupation is at hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/outro_completed"
msgid "The glorious 43rd Army completed the surrounding of Memel. During the offensive, the German 3rd Panzer Army HQ was overrun. Army Group North had been successfully trapped in North Courland."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/outro_failed"
msgid "This failure will prove very costly. The Germans now have the option to either reinforce or evacuate their 3rd Panzer Army! This means we will lose countless more comrades than we already have. You will be in the front echelon when we attack again!"
msgstr ""

